data.text:
Cheryl Fernandez-Versini Poses for David Roemer in Marie Claire UK Shoot

Cheryl’s New Name–With her new name, the former Cheryl Cole, poses as Cheryl Fernandez-Versini for the December 2014 cover story from Marie Claire UK. The X Factor judge and English singer goes minimal in the photo shoot captured by David Roemer of Atelier Management. On people using her old name, she tells the magazine, “People are so ignorant about it they just start calling us Cheryl, but I’ll take that, whatever.”

Photographer: David Roemer / Atelier Management | Talent: Cheryl Fernandez-Versini | Fashion Director: Jayne Pickering | Hair: Ali Pirzadeh | Make Up: Alex Babsky
